# Datasets and model artifacts — never commit
data/
*/data/
outputs/
*/outputs/
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt
*.stl
*.ply
*.obj

# ...but toothprint/bench/data is vendored CODE (data adapters), not a dataset — keep it
!toothprint/bench/data/
